Class KeywordAction

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.ityx.mediatrix.data.KeywordAction
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    KeywordList

    public class KeywordAction
extends Object
implements Serializable
    Describes a keyword action. In can be defined in the operator settings. If an operator performs an action(complete, requeue,...) the defined keywords will be inserted into Question.
